      <div class="info-card-desc">十二生肖排行第十</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <span class="info-card-icon">🔩</span>
      <div class="info-card-value">金</div>
      <div class="info-card-label">固定五行</div>
      <div class="info-card-desc">阴金——精密、雅致、明辨</div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-card">
      <span class="info-card-icon">🕔</span>
      <div class="info-card-value">酉 Yǒu</div>
      <div class="info-card-label">地支</div>
